  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a pixel-style classic tower defense game that incorporates roguelike elements. You need to summon souls to fend off enemy attacks, and each type of soul has its unique skill tree, with skills randomly selected upon upgrading. The game features an endless mode where you must achieve the highest score possible to unlock more skill trees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build your own unique maze.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 unique defense towers, each with their own specialized skills: Steal, Slow, Stun, Critical Hit, Multi-Arrows, Bloodthirst, Poison Arrows, Armor Reduction...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killing monsters increases your experience level. When you level up, you can randomly choose unique skills to build your own playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/99d9efd53d0a64926d1534113a11fbf5.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/99d9efd53d0a64926d1534113a11fbf5.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/99d9efd53d0a64926d1534113a11fbf5.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can adjust the difficulty of the levels to achieve higher scores.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/6c179da086929616dc6c846dacd3a05e.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/6c179da086929616dc6c846dacd3a05e.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/6c179da086929616dc6c846dacd3a05e.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Upgrade your skill tree for permanent boosts!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/b0b2073f19dfe64a714b6355fa5c1fad.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/b0b2073f19dfe64a714b6355fa5c1fad.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/b0b2073f19dfe64a714b6355fa5c1fad.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Achievement system: Unlock more Soul Artifacts and challenge higher difficulties!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/3cb8713c9930d03235ccaf1f20c2dc71.avif?t=1744450793\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras_big/3cb8713c9930d03235ccaf1f20c2dc71.avif?t=1744450793 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you're interested, add it to your wishlist! That way, I'll be more motivated to release more updates!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you have a better idea, please contact me by email! My </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a pixel-style classic tower defense game that incorporates roguelike elements. You need to summon souls to fend off enemy attacks, and each type of soul has its unique skill tree, with skills randomly selected upon upgrading. The game features an endless mode where you must achieve the highest score possible to unlock more skill trees.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can build your own unique maze.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 unique defense towers, each with their own specialized skills: Steal, Slow, Stun, Critical Hit, Multi-Arrows, Bloodthirst, Poison Arrows, Armor Reduction...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Killing monsters incr